questions.question: Have you read the 24/7 Channel Broadcaster Guide?
Are you 16 years of age or older?
Are you on the Streamers Connected Twitch Team?
Have you ever been suspended or banned on Twitch?

How long do you plan to commit to streaming to our 24/7 Twitch channel? You must commit to a minimum of 4 weeks to start, but you will be given the opportunity to continue streaming beyond that (in 4 week intervals) For EX: 4 Weeks, 8 Weeks, More than 8 Weeks, or As long as I can.
Why do you want to stream to our 24/7 Twitch channel?

welcome_message: Hello, welcome to this 24/7 stream application prompt.
